    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 2003 BMW M5 (E39), the definitive executive athlete. Under the hood, the S62 4.9L V8 utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver linear, high-revving power, mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual. This specimen retains its original factory-honed suspension geometry and a tight limited-slip differential. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of fatigue or oxidation, and the electronics\u2014including the notoriously fragile instrument cluster\u2014are fully functional. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this is a turnkey investment for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
