      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a showroom standard that exceeds even the most discerning expectations. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with zero stone chips or blemishes, preserved under a professional ceramic coating and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, featuring supple, crack-free leather, original protective floor mats, and a smoke-free environment. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous, full-service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic system functions perfectly, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
      "price": 44900.0,
